event_name: Wotagei Japanese light stick dancing with Ruriki
description:
The Wotagei class, taught by the radiant Ruriki, is a Japanese light stick dance. 

This dance style started off from fans as a way to cheer on their favorite idols and evolved to the current form which is known for it's wide stance and focus on using the light sticks to draw shapes with the light trails.

Do not worry about not having the light sticks on your avatar, the Temple will provide them.
